rentValue = e.target.value; setRentCar({...rentcar, [rentName]:rentValue}); } const handleRentFile = (e) =>{ const myrentfile = e.target.files[0] setRentFile({...rentcar, myrentfile}); } const postRentData = async (e) =>{ e.preventDefault();
